              a(href="/signup").btn.btn-secondary.px-3 Start doing →

  section.features-icons.bg-light.text-center
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-4
          .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
              i.icon-screen-desktop.m-auto.text-primary
            h3 Fully Responsive
            p.lead.mb-0 This theme will look great on any device, no matter the size!
        .col-lg-4
          .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
              i.icon-layers.m-auto.text-primary
            h3 Bootstrap 4 Ready
            p.lead.mb-0 Featuring the latest build of the new Bootstrap 4 framework!
        .col-lg-4
          .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
              i.icon-check.m-auto.text-primary
            h3 Easy to Use
            p.lead.mb-0 Ready to use with your own content, or customize the source files!

  section.showcase
    .container-fluid.p-0
      .row.no-gutters
        div(style="background-image: url('img/bg-showcase-1.jpg');").col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img
        .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text  
          h2 Fully Responsive Design
          p.lead.mb-0 When you use a theme created by Start Bootstrap, you know that the theme will look great on any device, whether it's a phone, tablet, or desktop the page will behave responsively!
      .row.no-gutters
        div(style="background-image: url('img/bg-showcase-2.jpg');").col-lg-6.text-white.showcase-img
        .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text  
          h2 Updated For Bootstrap 4
          p.lead.mb-0 Newly improved, and full of great utility classes, Bootstrap 4 is leading the way in mobile responsive web development! All of the themes on Start Bootstrap are now using Bootstrap 4!
      .row.no-gutters
        div(style="background-image: url('img/bg-showcase-3.jpg');").col-lg-6.order-lg-2.text-white.showcase-img
        .col-lg-6.order-lg-1.my-auto.showcase-text  
          h2 Easy to Use &amp; Customize
          p.lead.mb-0 Landing Page is just HTML and CSS with a splash of SCSS for users who demand some deeper customization options. Out of the box, just add your content and images, and your new landing page will be ready to go!

  section.testimonials.bg-light.text-center
    .container
      h2.mb-5 What people are saying...
      .row
        .col-lg-4
          .testimonials-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0
            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle.mb-3(src="img/testimonials-1.jpg" alt="")
            h5 Margaret E.
            p.font-weight-light.mb-0 "This is fantastic! Thanks so much guys!"
        .col-lg-4
          .testimonials-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0
            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle.mb-3(src="img/testimonials-2.jpg" alt="")
            h5 Fred S.
            p.font-weight-light.mb-0 "Bootstrap is amazing. I've been using it to create lots of super nice landing pages."
        .col-lg-4
          .testimonials-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0
            img.img-fluid.rounded-circle.mb-3(src="img/testimonials-3.jpg" alt="")
            h5 Sarah W.
            p.font-weight-light.mb-0 "Thanks so much for making these free resources available to us!"

  section.call-to-action.text-white.text-center
      .overlay
      .container
          .row
              .col-xl-9.mx-auto
                  h2.mb-4 Ready to get started? Sign up now!
              .col-md-10.col-lg-8.col-xl-7.mx-auto
                  form
                      .form-row
                          .col-12.col-md-9.mb-2.mb-md-0
                              input(type="email", name="", placeholder="Enter your email...")#femail.form-control.form-control-lg
                          .col-12.col-md-3
                              button(type="submit").btn.btn-block.btn-lg.btn-primary Sign up!
